Key Match Events: South Africa suffered a 13-run defeat at the hands of Netherlands
Colin Ackermann's late-hitting took Netherlands to 158/4
Brandon Glover returned with the figures of 3/9 in his two overs
Miscellaneous Highlights: India qualified for the semis after South Africa lost to Netherlands
Others: Either Pakistan or Bangladesh will join India as 2nd semi-finalist from Group 2
If the match gets washed out, then Pakistan will be through based on better net run rate
